nt tweets by the most popular tv series!</em> TvSeriesTweet is the new app for smartphones and tablets:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Follow the best and recent tweets from the best tv series</li>\n<li>You don&#8217;t even need a personal Twitter account</li>\n<li>More emphasis on words &amp; images (retweets &amp; replies are cut)</li>\n</ul>\n<p><span id="more-617"></span></p>\n<table>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td style="width: 50%;"><a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=it.whiletrue.tvseriestweet3" target="_blank"><img class="aligncenter colorbox-617" src="https://developer.android.com/images/brand/en_app_rgb_wo_60.png" alt="Android app on Google Play" /></a></td>\n<td style="width: 50%;"><a href="https://marketplace.firefox.com/app/polistweet/" target="_blank"><img class="aligncenter colorbox-617" src="https://marketplace.cdn.mozilla.net/media/img/mkt/badges/firefox-marketplace_badge-black_172_60.png?b=552b1c2-530f8025" alt="Firefox OS app" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style="width: 50%;"><a href="https://itunes.apple.com/it/app/tv-series-tweet/id963591758?mt=8" target="_blank"><img class="aligncenter colorbox-617" src="http://www.whiletrue.it/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/App-Store-Badge.png" alt="download from Apple Store" /></a></td>\n<td style="width: 50%;"><a href="http://windowsphone.com/s?appId=c86047da-e927-4e51-b96c-24b7998a7440" target="_blank"><img class="aligncenter colorbox-617" src="http://www.whiletrue.it/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/154x40_WPS_Download_blk.png" alt="download from Windows Phone Store" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p>◄ Always fresh ►</p>\n<ul>\n<li>View the most shared recent tweets, along with their shares count.</li>\n<li>Touch a tweet to instantly share it with your contacts.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>◄ Update &amp; Focus ►</p>\n<ul>\n<li>View and select the list of the leading and most active Tv Series on Twitter</li>\n<li>See the series actual influence value (changes day by day)</li>\n<li>Touch the Tv Series to read its best tweets, turn it off to hide its tweets.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<a href=''http://www.whiletrue.it/tvseriestweet/tvseriestweet_screenshot2/''><img width="150" height="150" src="http://www.whiletrue.it/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/tvseriestweet_screenshot2-150x150.png" class="attachment-thumbnail colorbox-617 " alt="tv series tweet" /></a>\n<a href=''http://www.whiletrue.it/tvseriestweet/screen/''><img width="150" height="150" src="http://www.whiletrue.it/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/screen-150x150.png" class="attachment-thumbnail colorbox-617 " alt="TvSeriesTweet" /></a>\n<a href=''http://www.whiletrue.it/tvseriestweet/tvseriestweet_screenshot1/''><img width="150" height="150" src="http://www.whiletrue.it/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/tvseriestweet_screenshot1-150x150.png" class="attachment-thumbnail colorbox-617 " alt="TvSeriesTweet on smartphone" /></a>\n<a href=''http://www.whiletrue.it/tvseriestweet/tvseriestweet_screenshot3/''><img width="150" height="150" src="http://www.whiletrue.it/wp-content/uploads/2014/04/tvseriestweet_screenshot3-150x150.png" class="attachment-thumbnail colorbox-617 " alt="TvSeriesTweet on tablet" /></a>\n\n<p>◄ Follow the Trend ► View the best hashtags and the most used words on Twitter by Tv Series accounts</p>\n<p>◄ Lots of Tv Series ► Featuring the best Tv Series, including: House of Cards, Game Of Thrones, Da Vinci&#8217;s Demons, Cosmos, How I met your mother, The Big Bang Theory, Hannibal, Orange Is the New Black, The Following, Helix, Teen Wolf, Scandal, Once: Wonderland, The Walking Dead, The Tomorrow People, Breaking Bad, 2 Broke Girls, Under The Dome, Black Sails, Brooklyn Nine-Nine, Almost Human, Masters of Sex, True Detective, The Killing, American Horror Story, Awkward, Glee, Pretty Little Liars, The Vampire Diaries, Falling Skies, True Blood etc.</p>\n<h3>Technical info</h3>\n<p>The app is made using HTML5 + Javascript and compiled with Cordova; the code was organized with Backbone (development framework) and the GUI with Ratchet 2.</p>\n<h3>News</h